{"tid":35567,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"戒賭兩個月，你問我答","createTime":"2016-12-12T07:22:32.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-12T16:31:00.000Z","uid":63107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6ee95d64dd462bcd30fe19f1baa4f0c2194e4cc7","tid":35567,"uid":63107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T07:22:32.000Z","msg":"輸最多嘅時候輸左一年有多嘅學費，希望巴打見到可以明白長賭必輸嘅道理，回頭是岸，由今日開始戒賭。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f135d83d740bbb5237b3d2b7b6e6e372e25eae8","tid":35567,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T07:23:51.000Z","msg":"幾時再賭？"},{"pid":"6b771e7ee7b359a596aea9c3b801686ea6388fda","tid":35567,"uid":63107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T07:26:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾時再賭？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n輸到驚左 唔會再大賭 最多細細地玩下"},{"pid":"a22f06ab97509a06e0f7fc367ce37024c8dc0085","tid":35567,"uid":63555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T07:29:02.000Z","msg":"總數輸左幾多？"},{"pid":"df18c316f528ff67be870d814adbc12b0cc4c7a7","tid":35567,"uid":55802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T07:30:34.000Z","msg":"而家負債幾多？"},{"pid":"13656fd8a9d11d877fe8634522f88d0e9547923f","tid":35567,"uid":63107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T07:30:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>總數輸左幾多？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\ntotal輸左&pound;6000左右，全盛時期輸大概&pound;24000"},{"pid":"9a55074437be5a5513be8e3fb4215fc6b9b425aa","tid":35567,"uid":63107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T07:32:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家負債幾多？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇負任何債 唯一興幸嘅地方 巴打賭錢一定要係自己能力範圍內賭 千其唔係問人借 只會輸更多 唔好信會翻身"},{"pid":"0d6b08a2e333b1157f86ed7cfd74d90aa6891684","tid":35567,"uid":63107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T07:47:52.000Z","msg":"希望個po唔好沉得咁快，等更多有賭癮嘅巴打睇到我嘅例子後成功戒賭"},{"pid":"f231c128666cb82d3debab67dec185b122cfe097","tid":35567,"uid":63107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T07:54:42.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"71658445618446d174b8eb0acbc0471701a9608e","tid":35567,"uid":61864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T07:55:49.000Z","msg":"我琴日西甲都輸左三百<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcb60db8f4521ac2ab6abf7a4091be76cdb0f656","tid":35567,"uid":55802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T07:56:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>而家負債幾多？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇負任何債 唯一興幸嘅地方 巴打賭錢一定要係自己能力範圍內賭 千其唔係問人借 只會輸更多 唔好信會翻身</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇負債已經好好，真係應該停。<br />\n我就負十幾，已經冇再賭，但都要還多幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00678663e0512fcd205636490c4f3b008b0a2cd0","tid":35567,"uid":63107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T07:59:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>而家負債幾多？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇負任何債 唯一興幸嘅地方 巴打賭錢一定要係自己能力範圍內賭 千其唔係問人借 只會輸更多 唔好信會翻身</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇負債已經好好，真係應該停。<br />\n我就負十幾，已經冇再賭，但都要還多幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打賭咩輸十幾個 我因為係外國 唔賭波 賭錢淨係去casino 輪盤輸得最多"},{"pid":"027047f02ecac5e69e41288c4454049b4717208c","tid":35567,"uid":63107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T08:00:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我琴日西甲都輸左三百<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n少賭宜情阿巴打 記得咪訓身"},{"pid":"4096c543f3da4e5a0ae8ff8c760e189c7d2f34aa","tid":35567,"uid":40245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T08:04:12.000Z","msg":"巴打。有咩心得 <br />\n我total輸左150k"},{"pid":"cfdb21e101b727f7f75592cde9f16bacbc82f6e2","tid":35567,"uid":384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T08:04:36.000Z","msg":"琴日入馬場輸左成千 仲讀緊書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n決心戒賭至到sem break翻工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a451e1e00e451a94c35a735b81f2ea7fac34455","tid":35567,"uid":63107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T08:12:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打。有咩心得 <br />\n我total輸左150k</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最後一次決心戒賭係因為上兩個月去賭場玩 &pound;3000嘅本 輸淨&pound;100，玩輪盤最後放左&pound;100係零到，點知真係岀左。變翻&pound;3500,之後玩百家樂，翻到&pound;12000,&pound;13000嘅時候唔走，最後連本金&pound;3000都輸埋。至此覺得輸左 就想追翻，贏左 就更加唔想走，想變大舊錢。輸曬之後岀左去食支煙，諗下其實個天唔係冇比過機會自己 係真係賭仔心態 所以決心戒賭"},{"pid":"704ea4f3b176582d77ce8fa1280a19039189938f","tid":35567,"uid":63107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T08:14:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>琴日入馬場輸左成千 仲讀緊書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n決心戒賭至到sem break翻工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n馬喱方面我真係完全冇認識，都係個句啦，少賭為妙阿巴打，回頭是岸。輪盤仲話有啲方法係易贏錢，馬我就真係冇乜認識"},{"pid":"edc495cd1579d1b93a0e6e87c7c47c4708416eca","tid":35567,"uid":63107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T08:36:52.000Z","msg":"大家幫手推下 希望更多人睇到喱個po"},{"pid":"97c5508cf1dc153158982c7b45ad611984075f8f","tid":35567,"uid":40245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T08:38:14.000Z","msg":"有冇方法 可以唔好有條癮￼"},{"pid":"5d971183335ed29272fbd3496383a409e8efe010","tid":35567,"uid":63107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T08:42:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇方法 可以唔好有條癮￼</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我個人玩輪盤就好鐘意就算唔玩 都睇住個盤心中面估，中左就同自己講啱啱個場用曬啲運氣 所以唔好再賭，唔中就直接諗好彩冇賭 慳翻。"},{"pid":"bc0478ed27b6548e125f4166341d7cf4bab16e8a","tid":35567,"uid":63107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T08:45:19.000Z","msg":"最誇張有斷時間為左近賭場 租左隔離酒店住左一個星期，除左訓教廿四粒鐘係賭場，因為我啲賭場積分根本上我食同飲一兩年係唔會用得曬"},{"pid":"a571dadb7da9ad87f18d7f775ee43a73c5967958","tid":35567,"uid":25389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T08:45:22.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aea17420a7916b0abdee199dbbb4a39e9b091cc","tid":35567,"uid":63107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T08:45:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔該曬巴打 希望幫到更多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf522d18d6d853ef8a74cf6ff99f3323e9d5b6aa","tid":35567,"uid":45769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T08:46:32.000Z","msg":"兩年前<br />\n玩股票輸左半個身家 <br />\n都有七八十個 全部辛苦錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n識到個好老婆<br />\n令我醒覺 慢慢儲返"},{"pid":"1bdaa7587da301387e427fcc8335b0ff24dba76d","tid":35567,"uid":6061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T08:50:16.000Z","msg":"仲記得以前諗住拿拿臨贏夠1m就收手打份hea工過下世算，每次都輸返轉頭。但轉左心態之後，每個月執返幾k洗用又幾順利，個人又輕鬆左無咁大上落"}]}